messages.text:
OK so it's already out there that they came loaded with cocaine. And wired.
There were terrorists who took tons of bullets and kept running like nothing happened.
They also found tons of drugs in vehicles and they were wired too. What madness, wow.
Are we talking about Belgium now?
The thousands that came in. They were all pumped with drugs.
The terrorists who infiltrated Israel were drugged?
Some of them. Definitely not all.
Maybe something else, but definitely war drugs.
It disconnects you, it's speed, I have no idea what specifically they brought with them, but stuff that helps you do things like that.
They planned this from every angle.
